{"id":102,"name":"At-Takathur","nameArabic":"التكاثر","transliteration":"At-Takathur","type":"meccan","ayahCount":8,"verses":[{"n":1,"text":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","translit":"Alhakumu alttakathuru","translation":"Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you"},{"n":2,"text":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","translit":"Hatta zurtumu almaqabira","translation":"Until you visit the graveyards"},{"n":3,"text":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","translit":"Kalla sawfa taAAlamoona","translation":"No! You are going to know"},{"n":4,"text":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","translit":"Thumma kalla sawfa taAAlamoona","translation":"Then no! You are going to know"},{"n":5,"text":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","translit":"Kalla law taAAlamoona AAilma alyaqeeni","translation":"No! If you only knew with knowledge of certainty"},{"n":6,"text":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","translit":"Latarawunna aljaheema","translation":"You will surely see the Hellfire"},{"n":7,"text":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","translit":"Thumma latarawunnaha AAayna alyaqeeni","translation":"Then you will surely see it with the eye of certainty"},{"n":8,"text":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","translit":"Thumma latusalunna yawmaithin AAani alnnaAAeemi","translation":"Then you will surely be asked that Day about pleasure"}]}